name: DPC 2023 NA Summer Tour Division I – presented by PGL
description:
Calling all Dota 2 fans in North America! Get ready for an action-packed tournament as the DPC 2023 Summer Tour is set to take place from May 15 to June 5. This tournament will feature top-tier teams from North America, battling it out for a chance to secure their spot in the third major of the season.

You won't want to miss a moment of the action as teams showcase their skills and strategies in thrilling matches. The DPC 2023 Summer Tour promises to be an unforgettable experience for Dota 2 fans in North America.

Get ready to support your favorite teams as they compete for a chance to make it to the next major!
